That&#x27;s incomplete in that it doesn&#x27;t automatically chdir back.  A proper block-scope &quot;with-&quot; macro will wrap the body in something like:<p><pre><code>    char *olddir = getcwd();
    chdir(newdir);
    try {
        do_stuff();
    } finally {
        chdir(olddir);
    }</code></pre>
